average of the premium index over the 8-hour period. The exchange caps funding rates at ±0.375% per cycle to prevent extreme market distortions. Funding fees are exchanged directly between long and short position holders, with Gate.io collecting no additional fees on funding transfers. Position holders must maintain their positions at the funding timestamp to pay or receive funding."}]]}],"$Lf",["$L10","$L11","$L12"],"$L13"]}],"$L14"]}]]}]
